  "instructions": [
    "Combine cannellini beans, smoked paprika, garlic, and ginger in a large bowl.",
    "Steam the mixture using a mushroom steam basket for 20 minutes, until the beans are tender.",
    "In a small pan, heat the coconut oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped green onions to the pan and saut\u00147 and cook for 2 minutes, until fragrant.",
    "Add the lime juice and stir to combine, then season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Pour the bean mixture into a serving bowl and top with the saut\u00147 and onions.",
    "Garnish with additional green onions if desired."
